args:
Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: We ended catch and release. We had Remain in Mexico, Title 42, Safe Third Agreements, and 500 miles of Border Wall. The final gaps of wall were about to be sealed—then Kamala came in, dismantled every single Trump Border policy, and halted wall construction.You can see on the ground behind me the sections of wall that taxpayers paid for but Kamala Harris refused to put up—because she wants the border wide open. What Biden and #ComradeKamala have done to the families here with me today is beyond shameful. It is evil.
